  <body>
    <div class="page-div">
      <h1 class="typewriter">The Void Plane</h1>
      <p class="typewriter">The Void Plane is a large non-euclidian construct than can be found outside of reality. It consists of many different regions that sometimes mimic human architecture. Each of these regions has its own unique look, feel and sometimes even physics. Regions can be traveled to and between via gateways. The true origin of the Void Plane remains unknown.</div>
      <a href="https://the-void-plane.neocities.org/archive/other.html" class="button-return">
        <div class="return-icon"></div>
        <p>Return to Other Entries</p>
      </a>
  </body>
</html>
